autolisp-spec-type-designators-and-nil-bottom — complete the TYPE designator dictionary; pin LIST = conses only; document NIL as bottom (⊥)
==========================================================================================================================================

See also:
  - autolisp-spec/documentation/autolisp-visual-lisp-specification-draft.org
    chapter 4, "* 4 Types and Runtime Classes" (line 1832) — the dictionary
    to complete.
  - same file:
